articles.title: Oilersnation Radio Episode 113 - Prospect watch, Reverse Retros, and Lali Toor from APNA Hockey
articles.description: It’s Friday afternoon and that means a brand new episode of Oilersnation Radio has been recorded, edited into a masterpiece, and ready to get you set for the weekend. This week, we looked at which Oilers prospects have us most excited, Reverse Retro jersey winners and losers, spoke to Lali Toor from APNA Hockey about winning the Willie O’Ree Community Hero Award, and a whole lot more.

articles.title: New Jersey man stole $90,000 before killing his brother and family, lawsuit says
articles.description: A New Jersey man charged with murdering four members of his family is accused of stealing $90,000 prior to their November 2018 deaths, according to a newly filed wrongful death lawsuit.

articles.title: LI judge won't release 911 calls in Gilgo Beach case
articles.description: A Long Island judge rejected the request from the family of victim Shannan Gilbert, a 24-year-old New Jersey escort whose decomposed remains were found in the Oak Beach marsh area in 2010.
articles.content: Gilbert was last seen running from the home of a man who lived near where her body was found. Her death has not conclusively been classified as a homicide. Police have suggested she drowned in the marsh....
